{"tid":2122385,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"濫捕濫告 【抗暴之戰 】反修例首宗暴動案審訊 赴湯杜火與少女暴動罪名不成立","createTime":"2020-07-24T03:26:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T04:31:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3c47dc318ffe91231b458fdfa19271149c2d06a0","tid":2122385,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:26:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200724/3SC7PECHMDUP45YRNJ6TZ3XSZA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200724%2F3SC7PECHMDUP45YRNJ6TZ3XSZA%2F&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6JFIS2qdHEMyYfCy%2BeARyBE%3D&h=65e28bf9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200724%2F3SC7PECHMDUP45YRNJ6TZ3XSZA%2F&h=80acee25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200724/3SC7PECHMDUP45YRNJ6TZ3XSZA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n濫捕濫告<br />\n【抗暴之戰 】反修例首宗暴動案審訊 赴湯杜火與少女暴動罪名不成立<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Izboywaxe7FyTQtHHGPUMPLU9LI=/640x359/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7W5HT3C37OKLGNOYOCGPEUIV2Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FIzboywaxe7FyTQtHHGPUMPLU9LI%3D%2F640x359%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7W5HT3C37OKLGNOYOCGPEUIV2Y.png&h=fb0e3a02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「赴湯杜火」夫婦湯偉雄（右）和杜依蘭<br />\n(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n去年7.28上環警民衝突，湯氏夫婦與一名少女被控當日參與暴動，案件早前審結，法官郭啟安今宣讀裁決，裁定三人暴動罪及交替的非法集結罪均罪名不成立，但夫婦兩人無牌管有一套無線對講機則罪成。夫婦二人聽聞裁決互相擁抱，於犯人欄內喜極而泣，杜依蘭亦與少女擁抱。公眾席上的親友聞判激動大聲哭泣，而散庭後，親友紛紛互相擁抱，並向三人的代表大狀道謝。<br />\n<br />\n湯氏夫婦約於審訊前半小時到達法庭，兩人走進視像庭向友人互相擊拳打招呼，夫婦笑言「一陣打邊爐呀」，友人亦回應「買定料等你」。今早支持者於早上6時多已開始於法院門外等候進庭，約八時半已有接近百人排隊以待索取入場證，所有入場證於開庭半小時前已派發完畢。<br />\n<br />\n被告為「赴湯杜火」夫婦。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n辯方早前陳詞指，被告夫婦當時只是扶起受傷的少女離開後巷；若控方認為上述行為亦屬集結及破壞秩序，是近乎天方夜譚。至於涉案少女，辯方指她當時被催淚煙燻至淚流滿臉、驚慌失措，逃跑只屬自然反應；即使她出於害怕警察而逃跑，亦不等同她是因犯罪而爬鐵欄。<br />\n<br />\n法官一度要求控方釐清其暴動罪指控的元素，又問控方是否「延伸」共同集結的定義、即被告的思想意圖與暴動者一致已屬集結。控方稱是，但承認沒有案例支持，亦沒有證據顯示兩名被告曾身處暴動現場。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：DCCC872/19 】<br />\n<br />\n----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n打國際線 《蘋果》英文版免費試睇 按此了解更多<br />\n英文版已登錄新版《蘋果》App按此下載/更新"},{"pid":"4b620d3f634fcb5c73b8a0d984252f0d6fb4f5f6","tid":2122385,"uid":19217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:50:14.000Z","msg":"制裁近 d官都正常d"},{"pid":"87577851247b94181c3121509b11cd619a2a05ac","tid":2122385,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:52:15.000Z","msg":"個律師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8a22b54b3ef64e5b13526cdefe0d778da4c9763","tid":2122385,"uid":180188,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:54:06.000Z","msg":"終於換返個正常D既官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5172fca9e412bb32c8616cbdaff2f2f3b87e771e","tid":2122385,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:55:04.000Z","msg":"杜依蘭亦與少女擁抱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw 少女有無俾狗咬??如果有又出庭聽審/證人, 咪即係自投羅網???"},{"pid":"f69c194356b09f337529dfd10abe1bcd555cef87","tid":2122385,"uid":156579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8a22b54b3ef64e5b13526cdefe0d778da4c9763","tid":2122385,"uid":180188,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:54:06.000Z","msg":"終於換返個正常D既官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:56:31.000Z","msg":"個官唔正常嫁<br />\n係唔知食錯咩藥定真係屈唔入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝潘大狀"},{"pid":"bf7e77940ba105692e9057ff685efb9ad9d0ff4d","tid":2122385,"uid":338439,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"cit